## First-Run Modal Version

**ClearSign is not a law firm and does not provide legal advice.**

The analysis you receive is generated by an AI and is provided for **educational and
informational purposes only**. It is not a substitute for advice from a licensed
attorney who knows the facts of your specific situation.

Using ClearSign does not create an attorney-client relationship between you and
ClearSign, its owners, or anyone affiliated with the service.

Contract law varies by jurisdiction, industry, and individual circumstance. An AI
analysis — including ours — cannot account for all the nuances of your situation or
local law.

**Before signing any contract with significant legal or financial consequences,
consult a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction.**

